SIMPLE: overblown
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: overblown
<hw>o`ver*blown"</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Having been given
more publicity than warranted; having had ascribed more importance than
was justified; <as>as, an <ex>overblown</ex> medical
discovery</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Bombastic, pretentious, or excessive; <as>as,
<ex>overblown</ex> rhetoric</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overboard</ent>⟦br⟧
